title: 20 Min Calisthenics Workout | No Equipment | All Levels
description:
Get ready for this 20 min full body Calisthenics workout which will prepare you for skills like the human flag, planche, any lever etc. The exercises target specifically the muscle groups engaged in these Calisthenics skills (and many more).

You can do this full body workout at home and without any equipment! No bars, no parallettes etc. needed. The only thing you need is yourself. Do every exercise with the full range of motion and focus on eccentric (negative) movements. This will boost your gains and progress tremendously.

Give your best - 40 sec full energy, 20 sec rest!
